steps.name: When  EzApp is launched and user enters VUL Insured details state and UL product
And  User Fills VUL LifeCase setup screen and NewYorkRegsixty when state is NY and click on Next
And  User Fills VUL Primary Insured and Primary Insured Cont screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills All VUL Personal History Information screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills VUL Life Product Screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills VUL Life Purpose of Insurance Screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills VUL Life Owner and Life Owner cont screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills EntityOwner and Trust Certification details Screen and click Next
And  User Fills VUL Life Beneficiaries and Other Coverage screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills VUL Life Payment Information and Certification screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills VUL HIV consent screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills VUL Life Producer Statement screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills VUL Life Producer Compensation screen details and click on Next
And  User Selects Additional Forms details and click Next
And  User attaches VUL required docs in the Attachments Screen and click on Next
Then  Lock the Policy and do Wet or E sign for VUL as Required
